OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FThe sister of one of disgraced surgeon
OL,8,FIan Paterson's patients has said she
OL,9,Fis "relieved" the "horrible" wait for
OL,10,Fher sister's inquest is over, more
OL,11,Fthan a year after it was originally
OL,12,Fmeant to be heard.
OL,14,FMarie Pinfield, who was a Child
OL,15,FProtection Officer at West Midlands
OL,16,FPolice, died at the age of 50 in 2008,
OL,17,Fafter being operated on by Paterson in
OL,18,FBirmingham.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FShe had been diagnosed with advanced
OL,8,Fbreast cancer, and, despite asking for
OL,9,Fa double mastectomy, was subject to an
OL,10,Funregulated operation by Paterson,
OL,11,Fwhere he left breast tissue behind.
OL,13,FMarie went on to develop secondary
OL,14,Fcancer in her lungs and died two
OL,15,Fmonths later.
OL,17,F"I did my best for you"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FSpeaking outside court, Marie's sister
OL,8,FSharon Moroney said she was "relieved"
OL,9,Fthe inquest was finally happening and
OL,10,Fhoped it would lead to closure.
OL,12,FShe said "I know now that I'll be able
OL,13,Fto meet her on the other side, look
OL,14,Fher in the eye, and say 'I did it,
OL,15,FMarie. I did my best for you".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FPaterson is currently serving a 20-
OL,8,Fyear prison sentence after being found
OL,9,Fto have carried out unnecessary and
OL,10,Funapproved procedures, on more than a
OL,11,Fthousand breast cancer patients over
OL,12,F14 years.
OL,14,FThe consultant breast surgeon was
OL,15,Femployed by the Heart of England NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust and practised in the
OL,17,Findependent sector at Spire Parkway
OL,18,Fand Spire Little Aston, all in
OL,19,FBirmingham between 1997 and 2011.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FHe was convicted of 17 counts of
OL,8,Fwounding with intent and three counts
OL,9,Fof unlawful wounding, and was
OL,10,Fsentenced in 2017.
OL,12,FPaterson did not show up for the first
OL,13,Fday of the inquest, which Ms Moroney
OL,14,Fsaid left her extremely disappointed.
OL,16,FShe said: "I could feel my anger
OL,17,Fbuilding, because from a mental health
OL,18,Fpoint of view... you really do want to
OL,19,Ffeel that (Paterson) has heard the
OL,20,Fsuffering you've gone through."
OL,26,@xD@KOU{D@Kpm{D@Tpn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FShirley Moroney gave about details of
OL,8,Fappointments she'd attended with her
OL,9,Fsister in the run-up to two surgeries
OL,10,Fcarried out in September and October
OL,11,F2006 - two years before her death.
OL,13,FShirley recalled how during an
OL,14,Fappointment despite her sister asking
OL,15,Ffor a double mastectomy, she says
OL,16,FPatterson said that is not what she
OL,17,Fwould want. She also said during one
OL,18,Fappointment he was intimidating
OL,19,Ftowards her sister.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FPaterson gave evidence today via a
OL,8,Fvideo link from prison and said his
OL,9,Ffocus was on removing the cancer in
OL,10,FMarie Pinfield's left breast.
OL,12,FShirley recalls "she had a nagging
OL,13,Ffeeling in the back of her mind that
OL,14,Fhe - Mr Patterson - wasn't going to be
OL,15,Flistening to her sister."
OL,17,FShe says after the first operation and
OL,18,Fthe second, it was clear Patterson
OL,19,Fhadn't carried out the surgery Marie
OL,20,Fhad asked for.
OL,26,@tD@QO]wD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FThe court was also shown pictures
OL,8,Fshowing the scarring on her breasts
OL,9,Fafter both surgeries were carried out.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FMarie's case is one of a series of
OL,17,Finquests examining the deaths of 62
OL,18,Fformer patients of Paterson, which may
OL,19,Fhave been unnatural.
OL,21,FMany are still waiting to be heard.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FMs Moroney said "It's horrible for all
OL,8,Fthe people who are still waiting...
OL,9,Fbut at least we're here".
OL,11,FThe series of inquests began at
OL,12,FBirmingham Coroner's Court in October
OL,13,F2024, after a 2020 inquiry heard
OL,14,FPaterson had been carrying out an
OL,15,Funapproved version of a mastectomy,
OL,16,Fleaving some breast tissue behind.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FIt was paused a few months later,
OL,8,Fhowever, after Paterson raised
OL,9,Fconcerns that one of the medical
OL,10,Fexperts on the inquests'
OL,11,Fmultidisciplinary team (MDT) had shown
OL,12,Fbias and that their evidence should be
OL,13,Fexcluded.
OL,15,FHe cited an email from one of the MDT
OL,16,Fexperts, professor and consultant
OL,17,Fbreast surgeon Mike Dixon, in which he
OL,18,Fwrote to another member: "We need to
OL,19,Ffind some way though of exposing
OL,20,FPaterson as a liar and an incompetent
OL,21,Fsurgeon."
OL,26,@zD@ZOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776798669
OL,3,CSister of Ian Paterson patient says
OL,4,Cinquest delay 'horrible' as hearing
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FWhile the email was "unfortunate,
OL,8,Finappropriate and clumsy", Judge
OL,9,FFoster said, it was not by itself
OL,10,Findicative of actual or unconscious
OL,11,Fbias.
OL,13,FDespite this, he concluded Professor
OL,14,FDixon should withdraw from the MDT for
OL,15,Fthe purposes of the ongoing inquiries.
OL,17,FPublic and private hospitals Paterson
OL,18,Fworked for have already paid out
OL,19,Fmillions of pounds in compensation.
OL,21,FThe inquest continues.
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
